WEBVTT

22:23.630 --> 22:25.000 line:80%
Just because a bad guy scared me
with a stick,

22:25.000 --> 22:27.330 line:80%
does that mean
I should be scared to death?

22:27.720 --> 22:29.540 line:80%
But your husband...

22:29.680 --> 22:31.340 line:80%
He was quite scary that night.

22:31.480 --> 22:33.010 line:80%
He's not usually like that.
